videos.description: Villanova's Collin Gillespie throws a nice bounce pass along the baseline to Donte DiVincenzo for the layup.
videos.headline: Gillespie's sweet pass leads to DiVincenzo lay-in

videos.description: Northern Iowa guard Tywhon Pickford misses the 3-point shot, but gets his own miss and goes in for the layup.
videos.headline: Panthers Pickford misses shot, but gets own miss for lay-in

videos.description: Villanova guard Jalen Brunson hits a 3-pointer despite the contest.
videos.headline: Brunson drills 3-pointer with hand in his face

videos.description: Northern Iowa's Spencer Haldeman drills the corner 3-pointer after faking out Villanova guard Jalen Brunson
videos.headline: Haldeman fakes Brunson out, drills fade away 3-pointer

videos.description: Villanova guard Jalen Brunson saves the possession by throwing it off Northern Iowa's Bennett Koch and dives over the Panther's water boy.
videos.headline: Brunson throws ball off UNI, takes out water boy

videos.description: Villanova forward Eric Paschall drives to the hoop and delivers a strong dunk to give the Wildcats a 44-33 lead.
videos.headline: Paschall throws down thunderous dunk for Nova

videos.description: Villanova shows off the ball movement with the extra pass to Phil Boothe in the corner for the open 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Villanova  uses extra pass to drill corner three

videos.description: Villanova's Jalen Brunson throws a cross court pass out of the corner to Mikal Bridges for a wide open 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Brunson's great pass leads to back-breaking 3-pointer for Nova

videos.description: Karl Ravech and Dick Vitale break down how Villanova avoided upsets and the play of Mikal Bridges and Jalen Brunson.
videos.headline: Vitale: Villanova can make a lot of noise

videos.description: Four of Villanova's starters score in double figures as the Wildcats improve to 6-0 with a 64-50 win over Northern Iowa.
videos.headline: Villanova tops Northern Iowa to stay undefeated
